<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading2"><h2 id=3D"Endomorphisms_and_square_ma=
trices">Endomorphisms and square matrices</h2><span class=3D"mw-editsection=
"><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href=3D"https://en.wiki=
pedia.org/w/index.php?title=3DLinear_algebra&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;section=
