ar <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">a</span> in <s=
pan class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">F</span>. This scal=
ar <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">a</span> is an=
