al">double dual</a></b> or <b><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bidu=
al" class=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"Bidual">bidual</a></b> of <span class=3D=
"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">V</span>. This canonical map is=
 an <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Isomorphism" title=3D"Isomorph=
ism">isomorphism</a> if <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:it=
alic;">V</span> is finite-dimensional, and this allows identifying <span cl=
